 Connector settings

The OSGi Config Admin stores Cloud Connector configuration (enabled state,
exposed items, base URL) in userdata/config. Without persisting it, the
Cloud connection breaks on restart even with UUID/secret preserved.

Now 14 granular subPath mounts total.
